addMissingAsync.title: Add Missing `async` Keyword
addMissingAsync.description: Adds the missing `async` keyword where a promise should be returned.

addMissingAwait.title: Add Missing `await` Keyword
addMissingAwait.description: Adds the missing `await` keyword where a promise should be returned but not being properly handled.

addMissingAwaitToInitializer.title: Add `await` To Intializers
addMissingAwaitToInitializer.description: Adds missing `await` keyword to declarations and expressions.

addMissingConstraint.title: Add Missing Type Constraint
addMissingConstraint.description: Adds an `extends` keyword to constrain a generic type parameter.

addMissingInvocationForDecorator.title: Add Declaration For Decorator
addMissingInvocationForDecorator.description: Turns decorators into invocations where appropriate.

addMissingNewOperator.title: Add `new` Operator
addMissingNewOperator.description: Adds `new` operator where it is needed.

addOptionalPropertyUndefined.title: Add Optional Property
addOptionalPropertyUndefined.description: Adds `undefined` to the type of an optional field.

addVoidToPromise.title: Add `void` To Promise
addVoidToPromise.description: Adds the `void` as the type parameter of `Promise` where appropriate.

constructorForDerivedNeedSuperCall.title: Add Super To Constructor
constructorForDerivedNeedSuperCall.description: Adds a call the super class within the constructor.

convertToTypeOnlyExport.title: Convert To Type Export
convertToTypeOnlyExport.description: Adds `type` to exports where the entity(s) that is exported is a type(s).

convertTypedefToType.title: Convert @typedef to Type
convertTypedefToType.description: Converts JSDoc typedef to TypeScript type(s).

convertToTypeOnlyImport.title: Convert to Type Only Import
convertToTypeOnlyImport.description: Adds `type` to imports where the entity(s) being imported are type(s).

deleteUnmatchedParameter.title: Delete Unused Parameter
deleteUnmatchedParameter.description: Deletes parameters that are documented but not in the implementation.

extendsInterfaceBecomesImplements.title: Convert `extends` To `implements` On Interfaces
extendsInterfaceBecomesImplements.description: Converts `extends` to `implements` when interfaces are extended but empty.

fixAwaitInSyncFunction.title: Adds `await` To Sync Function
fixAwaitInSyncFunction.description: Add async modifier to containing function.

fixCannotFindModule.title: Cannot Find Module
fixCannotFindModule.description: Attempts to download type modules for modules that can not be resolved.

fixEnableJsxFlag.title: Enable JSX
fixEnableJsxFlag.description: When JSX is detected, enable the tsconfig configuration for JSX.

fixImportNonExportedMember.title: Fix Import Of Non-Exported Member
fixImportNonExportedMember.description: Modifies the file that is being imported to expose the correct members.

fixMissingAttributes.title: Add Missing Attribute
fixMissingAttributes.description: Adds an attribute to a JSX element if it missing.

fixMissingMember.title: Fix Missing Member
fixMissingMember.description: Ensures that there is a type or implementation associated with a member.

fixMissingProperties.title: Add Missing Property
fixMissingProperties.description: Adds properties that are missing from objects.

fixOverrideModifier.title: Fix Override Modifier
fixOverrideModifier.description: Adds the `override` modifier where the subclass is overriding the method.

fixReturnTypeInAsyncFunction.title: Fix Return Type Of Async Functions

inferFromUsage.title: Infer From Usage
inferFromUsage.description: Infers the types based on how the value is being used.

invalidImportSyntax.title: Invalid Import Syntax
invalidImportSyntax.description: Fixes issues related to assignability of imports.

jdocTypes.title: Add Types From JSDoc
jdocTypes.description: Annotates code with the types from the declared JSDoc comments.

removeUnnecessaryAwait.title: Remove Unnecessary Await
removeUnnecessaryAwait.description: Removes `await` where the function is not async.

strictClassInitialization.title: Strict Class Initialization
strictClassInitialization.description: Fixes classes so they are initialized correctly.

addErrorTypeGuard.title: Add Error Cast
addErrorTypeGuard.description: Adds a cast to Error objects in catch clauses

addMissingTypesBasedOnInheritance.title: Add Missing Types From Inheritance Chain
addMissingTypesBasedOnInheritance.description: Adds types to sub-class by looking at the types from the heritage.

makeMemberOptional.title: Make Member Optional
makeMemberOptional.description: Safely makes the access to properties optional.

addMissingExport.title: Add Missing Export
addMissingExport.description: Exports members that are required and used by other exports.

inferReturnType.title: Add Missing Return Type
inferReturnType.description: Adds the return type to methods and functions.

annotateWithStrictTypeFromJSDoc.title: Annotate Strict Types From JSDoc
annotateWithStrictTypeFromJSDoc.description: Annotates code with the only strict types from the declared JSDoc comments.
